    • compareTo

      public int compareTo(Tag o)
      Compare this tag to another one for ordering. Note: this class has a natural ordering that is inconsistent with equals; ordering is by the tag ID only (this is fine for tags obtained from the same chip at the same time, which is the primary use case).
